{"type": "article", "id": 24528, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 25461, "name": "LimeLAB"}, {"id": 25462, "name": "Lagranja"}, {"id": 24156, "name": "Siegenthaler & Co"}, {"id": 25078, "name": "Louie Rigano"}, {"id": 25463, "name": "Libero Rutilo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104132mpKacWkV0R6obCrA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Interface Table by Louie Rigano</h2>\n<p>上周我们介绍过美国设计师 Louie Rigano “印出树影的窗帘”，这是他最新设计的桌子。他使用了有波纹的玻璃纤维板作为桌面、支柱和隔板，不同面之间都像积木一样相互拼接，玻璃的转折之间形成了微妙的光影变化，很轻盈。桌面上另有一块与波纹桌面相嵌的移动木板，可以放杯子等茶具。<a href=\"http://www.louierigano.com/Interface-Table\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153840YruiGeZXOnNo0P23.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153841sQrIhfocCiuAjB1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153841f0TzYeCvxqBs984y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153842fF7jkIs0evXJ81qz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153843OeGtbPC6sKUSAahj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>THE DAYLIGHT DESK LAMP by LimeLAB</h2>\n<p>这盏弯曲的台灯在形态上像一条蛇，也令人想起维纳·潘顿的“S”型椅，一张试图用一块板材制造出一把有完整外壳的椅子。台灯的底座使用氯丁橡胶（Neoprene）材料，底座是一个轻微的转折并与桌面形成了三角空间，很稳定。台灯的支柱是逐渐变细的，流畅的曲线让这盏灯保持了轻盈。而最上面连接了一个圆形的小灯，灯光柔和。这盏灯产自意大利，有 7 种颜色选择，售价 199 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.limelab.it/shop-eur/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153844FSjUvRTXbsOqPucZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153845KvoxOql1gPV9QbtE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071538462ZAVWrPkhOzmoxwM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153846qpPX1lwYDbfTao5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153847urcnzSyU1YI9fwaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>3D PRINT YOUR VASE by Libero Rutilo</h2>\n<p>将塑料瓶废物利用做成花瓶并不新鲜，但往往也没什么美观可言。米兰的设计师 Libero Rutilo 的设计重点在于瓶子外的黑色的“壳”，他做了 4 种 3D 打印的网状的壳，有的像钻石的纹路，有的是蜘蛛网格，还有的模拟了陶瓷花瓶的流畅曲线，罩在盛满水的塑料瓶外面就像真的有一个玻璃花瓶一样。一点简单的改变就可以让生活有趣味。<a href=\"http://www.designlibero.com/portfolio/3d-printed-vases-collection/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153847dGDK2asHu7W0xUpA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153850mhlRcrnvYJk80tFV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153850avl3m5fnYJdsj86U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153851GEAIJg4byqzoFLaR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153852da3jZzuSEtxl7CJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>UMBRELLOCKED by 张硕 &amp; 戴少云 &amp; 王文年</h2>\n<p>雨伞也许是最容易丢失的生活用品之一，这几个中国设计师在雨伞的把手上设计了密码锁。仅仅是在弯曲把手的最外面安装一个可伸缩的密码锁，需要时将它拔出来形成一个闭合环，类似自行车车锁，简易且方便。产品目前还没上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153852subeQVgmyc8woUnI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153853cPQXFmC4TAdUVzrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153854f2anC49ji0MHSJOQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cooking Tableware by Toshiba &amp; Lagranja</h2>\n<p>这组陶瓷茶具来自西班牙设计工作室 Lagranja，包括水壶、罐子和可加热的无线感应底座。水壶把手和底座的边缘都是木质的，搭配白色的磁壶，突出了茶具的简洁。而圆形底座也让加热变得方便且美观。设计师想要让这些存在于厨房的工具也能运用于客厅等场所，以此适应越来越小的居住空间。<a href=\"http://lagranjadesign.com/cooking-tableware/?lang=en\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153855TMuqaBVIgUeNEFdW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79681275\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153857J7bwsCd4IHhcLiFr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153857yLQbePoXIAi29ulj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153858xaRgesNdZ1McIVnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153859WyogNRfPT9JUvHtG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>MASA TAKE AWAY BAGS by Siegenthaler &amp; Co</h2>\n<p>这组装面包袋子的包装来自哥伦比亚平面设计 Siegenthaler &amp; Co，是为当地一家老的面包品牌 MASA 重新设计的。他们将面包本身的黑白照片放到了包装袋上，使得在大街上也能拥有吸引力，似乎透过了图片看到了里面松软可口的面包。此外，每组包装除了黑、白色外都会使用一种彩色，都是天蓝、橙黄这样清新而活泼的颜色，保持了简洁干净和年轻的特征。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153900kwfAjga9Wi1Rosyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153902yUaxCD9ZtneQdVGm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153902r8gSoe6U1wd3hvkC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071539043WfSXInueh5B6q8p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153904JXOreRTdKz0yhN6u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153905N80Kc3M9SbTYyp56.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}